column1: #Text="Then again i went to another eye specialist. he advised me to put cold compresses on my eyes with ice. twice daily morning and evening. he said i had got derbis collected on my eyebrows and he gave me same refresh tears eye drops and one antibiotic drops which clears derbis from my eyes. i took his treatment for two months. it did not helped me. after two months i had went to another eye doctor she prescribed my same refresh tears eye drops and one ointment called ""Tetracycline Hydrochloride Ointment"". her (third doctor's) treatment also did not help me. i left all drops and ointments. and started ramdev baba's eye drops. i used it for 3 to 4 months. it also did not help me. i had search on internet and find that himalaya company also has one eye drops i used that also, after that i had used homeopathy eye drop also. but unfortunately nothing had helped me. i was in severe depression because of my problems. still i was skipping meals. and also holding urine. my health problems getting worse. i tried many homeopathy medicines and ayurvedic medicines like ""amalky rasayan, triphala ghrita, triphala churna"", etc. i started losing weight. i was 23 years old at that time and i am looking like i am 30 years old. i started getting angry on my family members. i had got appetite. i don't like to eat anything. what ever was cooked at home i started abusing them that they"
